     C* Conditioned execution via result indicators.
     C* T = 0 + 5 = 5 (positive) => indicator 50 ON => RPGRET = 100
     C* Expected exit code = 100
     C                     Z-ADD5         RPGRET
     C                     Z-ADD0         T
     C                     ADD  5         T          50
     C  50                 Z-ADD100       RPGRET
